il barna dine at du ikke stoler p\u00e5 dem, sier hun."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "forbruker"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "3f565f069604679a79f83aab7f43b03a047ce4ebc687ea9c74e301bcdec2ecd5"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2017-02-25T20:17:44.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Ved \u00e5 utstyre barnet ditt med en bamse med innebygd overv\u00e5kningskamera, invaderer du barnets privatliv."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article1235724.ece5/ALTERNATES/w980-default/guro_sk%C3%A5ltveit2"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/6867dd0f5640e6d0185afcd764eb4151f98adaa6.jpg?593bcc5d"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["- Invaderer barnas privatliv -adressa.no", "Barnets bamse", "Invaderende"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "6867dd0f5640e6d0185afcd764eb4151f98adaa6"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["nyheter", "trondheim", "ukeadressa", "eadressa", "skattelister", "d\u00f8dsfall", "tr\u00f8nder", "trafikk"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "nyheter,trondheim,ukeadressa,eadressa,skattelister,d\u00f8dsfall,tr\u00f8nder,trafikk"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": "forbruker"}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "family-and-parenting"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["barn", "barnas privatliv", "invaderer barnas privatliv"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["eblaster", "internett", "datatilsynet", "guro sk\u00e5ltveit"]}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-taxonomy", "value": "forbruker"}, {"field": "og-image", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article1235724.ece5/ALTERNATES/w980-default/guro_sk%C3%A5ltveit2"}, {"field": "og-locale", "value": "nb_NO"}, {"field": "og-site-name", "value": "adressa.no"}, {"field": "og-title", "value": "- Invaderer barnas privatliv"}, {"field": "og-type", "value":